      "text": "For whatever reason, I was able to work out my transgression at NYU in [[Haley Mellin]]'s undergraduate senior thesis course. This was very off the books: Mellin would meet me before class started in order to let me in through the backdoor of the Steinhardt building. The course requirement was that everybody had to do a thesis, and find someone in the art world that they didn't know to come to class and talk about whatever the class wanted to talk about. So that was the art world I was introduced to: the one you could email, not the one that gave you a solo show your senior year. "
